         VERSION=1.3.27
     SOURCE_HASH=sha512:bc10bc715a4891c5e0004abf343eef8ab6dedf5f4f33eca46e21db4ad711d931c12bc163b04f5d9eac63571f631efc65bde0d0c84cc4d53a8b78125f3ec9b607
